snippet.title: DISNEY To Remove JACK SPARROW From Theme Parks | Johnny Depp \ Amber Heard Court Drama To Blame
snippet.description:
#Disney #PiratesOfTheCaribbean #Johnny Depp

In this episode of Jolly's Rants, Jolly  discusses the latest rumor of cancel culture taking over Disneyland and Disneyworld and the possible removal of Jack Sparrow from The Pirates of the Caribbean ride.

Check out #20 on Jolly's Top Scary Movie Countdown
